snippet.title: Good Lord! Visual Novel Trailer
snippet.description:
"Good Lord! Everyone at the Reunion For My Religious All-Girls School Is a Trans Man... And They're Hot?!" is out now on itch.io FOR FREE!

https://whatnames.itch.io/good-lord

Good Lord is a romantic comedy otome game featuring a cast of all trans masculine love interests. Catch up with your old graduating class and maybe learn a thing or two about yourself in a hilarious weekend romp at a posh vineyard. What could possibly go wrong?

Made by:
Writer (Elias Route) - Avior (he/him)
Writer (Angel Route) - BáiYù (he/they)
Writer (Liam Route) - Shamus Kelley (he/him)
Editor - Spookybot (he/him)
Art - Stem (they/them)
Composer - Kris Kirk (he/him)
Logo Designer - Kyla Aiko (she/they)
Tools Programmer - Pawlik (any)
Lead Programmer - Runa Liore (she/her)
Sensitivity Consultant - Els White (he/him) and lacyspaceycasey (she/they)
Director and Producer - WhatNames (all)

#GoodLordVN
